    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The faculty members are so friendly and teach well.",
          "name": "Monica K",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like our college placement because they give 90% placement with average 8 lakhs per annum",
          "name": "ANBUCHEZHIYAN D",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Labs for are seperate blocks , college food",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "course explanation and faculty, support staff support",
          "name": "Rehan Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Quality of education is good and many workshops had been conducted",
          "name": "Rajeswari M",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Faculties support for our placements and good teaching",
          "name": "Divesh Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The lab facilities are equipped but not up to the mark in some departments",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Thirdly, I really like the efforts they put on placements. They sign with top organizations for the placement trainings and even make the students spend their whole semester for placement training.",
          "name": "Kishore",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Student are focused only on syllabus and no extra activities are encouraged.",
          "name": "Monica K",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "No culturals, no function, no celebration.",
          "name": "ANBUCHEZHIYAN D",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "campus recruitment is low and some new recruitment should have increased",
          "name": "Rehan Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "network availablity in campus would be low",
          "name": "Rehan Kumar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Rare conduction of Culturals , symposium",
          "name": "Rajeswari M",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "They have supervisors in every floor but if there was some money stolen by ur cls mates or someone took it. They say they don't know.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Lack of professional staffs. From the first semester I've been seeing a lot of Professors and Asst. Professors without the proper knowledge of what they gonna teach the students.",
          "name": "Kishore",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no co Ed in the college campus, seperate class for boys and girls",
          "name": "Gowtham",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Moreover, the poor placement opportunities for MBA students are a significant drawback of the college, limiting career prospects and opportunities for professional growth.",
          "name": "S K Swamy",
          "course_tag_name": "MBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Addressing these issues would contribute to a more inclusive and supportive educational environment for all students.",
          "name": "S K Swamy",
          "course_tag_name": "MBA"
        }
      ]
    },
